USER:  
get /user -> erhält aktuellen user  
Null
200 { "username":<string>, "email":<string> }
403 forbidden: no user logged in

post /user -> erzeugt user
{ "username":<string> , "email":<string> , "password":<string> }
200 success
400 username already exists
400 bad symbols in username
400 email exists
400 wrong email format
400 insecure password

post /user/login   
{ "email":<string>, "password":<string> }  
200 success
400 invalid email or password  

post /user/logout  
Null  
200 success


